cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.DC, cs.NE 

The paper is about a fast encoder for visual search using CDVS standard. The paper leverages GPU for parallel execution and optimization of memory access. This suggests that the paper could belong to the following categories: Multimedia (cs.MM), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Graphics (cs.GR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
